↓

Validate

- Active period
- Purchase limit
- Inventory

↓

Select shipping address

↓

Confirm purchase

↓

Deduct Gems

↓

Create Order

↓

Create Order Item

↓

Reserve Inventory

↓

Create Inventory Transaction (Reserved)

↓

Create Shipping Information

↓

