```

---

# Fulfillment Flow

```
Admin

↓

Prepare Shipment

↓

Update Shipping Status

↓

Ship Package

↓

Deliver Package

↓

Create Inventory Transaction (StockOut)

↓

Complete Order
```

Shipping Status and Order Status are managed independently.

